{"tid":1160283,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[估地方]逆女帶損友歸家，向老父索要珠寶不果，朋黨憤而殺父","createTime":"2019-05-18T11:10:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-18T11:43:29.000Z","uid":22633,"like":34,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f68b053b3479dc824bd9c3475c683111f7f12bf6","tid":1160283,"uid":22633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T11:10:55.000Z","msg":"[本報訊]日前一名獨居長者，<br />\n被發現斷頭倒臥家中，死狀恐怖，<br />\n據稱事發地點為老人退休養老地方，<br />\n老人多年前收養兩個女孤兒，視如己出，惜收養的長女早年意外墮樓身亡，剩下收養的二女與老人相依為命，<br />\n惜二女生性反叛，喜結交損友，未幾離家剩老父一人生活，<br />\n案發當日據報二女新結識的朋友得知事主收藏為數不少寶石，見獵心起，<br />\n逆女竟帶同一堆損友，登門向事主索要寶石，隨行更有人攜帶武器，<br />\n當時事主獨自一人在家準備晚餐，眾人突然闖入並發生爭執糾纏，有人為威逼事主說出收藏下落竟用斧頭砍下事主左手，<br />\n及發發現威逼不果，疑知道事主手上並無值錢財物，竟冷血砍下事主頭顱後逃去，<br />\n當地警方呼籲當日有目睹案發一干人等的市民主動聯絡提供資料<br />\n<br />\n事主及逆女照片（慎入！）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n逆女<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9c4pZLQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9c4pZLQ.png&h=788bfbe0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n老父<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LQFTS5H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLQFTS5H.png&h=4cb7e9d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3152a9f599a7977584ce82c58c59b401ff0ce29c","tid":1160283,"uid":94828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T11:22:34.000Z","msg":"我識佢 佢以前唔係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77c9c6903cc49df64b09d1c43dce2558ddedfbfe","tid":1160283,"uid":71579,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T11:27:07.000Z","msg":"5.5/10"},{"pid":"0166e9356ef7a9fb70c1344145705ab7e82d0e8d","tid":1160283,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T11:29:25.000Z","msg":"估錯咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fbee0e16923ecf8a9aeea861edfd814a5a31cd7","tid":1160283,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T11:39:44.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"1b0e121d7737a428185330c08ac0a5607537e5d1","tid":1160283,"uid":22633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0166e9356ef7a9fb70c1344145705ab7e82d0e8d","tid":1160283,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T11:29:25.000Z","msg":"估錯咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T11:43:29.000Z","msg":"渣ga <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}